  <summary>A productivity timer application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Flow Focus is a productivity timer application that helps you stay focused and manage your
      work sessions effectively.
      It uses the Pomodoro Technique to break work into focused intervals, separated by short
      breaks.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Customizable work and break intervals</li>
      <li>Desktop notifications</li>
      <li>Dark and light theme support</li>
    </ul>
